data.description: This stunning, fully rebuilt home in 2021 features a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout on an expansive oversized lot. Every aspect is brand new, from the stainless steel appliances to the stylish vinyl plank flooring that spans the entire home. Say goodbye to carpets, HOA fees, and enjoy the benefit of low taxes. Ideal for a first-time homebuyer or as an investment property, this beautiful home promises to be a lucrative income-generating asset.
